Category:Imperial Navy pilots of the Galactic Empire

nodes.text: "Deathfire" was a TIE pilot active during the Galactic Civil War. Deathfire often piloted a TIE/sa bomber, and was specifically a member and veteran of Gamma Squadron. As the handle implied, Deathfire often dropped a salvo of proton bombs on the enemy.
